casebody.data:
RAUBICHECK, Respondent v. SNEDECOR, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 5, 1894.) Appeal from city court, general term. Action by Frank Raubicheck against William V. Snedecor.

Argued before BOOKSTAVER, BISCHOFF, and PRYOR, JJ.

Niles & Johnson, for appellant. H. R. Squier, for respondent.

No opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs. See 25 N. Y. Supp. 1145.
